    "accordion_K3YKGe": {
      "type": "accordion",
      "blocks": {
        "accordion_pane_KaBdPe": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How durable are the spring suits for water sports?",
            "content": "<p>Our spring suits are designed with high-performance Eco-neoprene and feature triple-glued, blind-stitched seams to withstand the rigors of active water sports. Whether you’re surfing, paddleboarding, or diving, these suits are built to last season after season.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_pane_cYX4Eg": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What makes the Mentawai women’s wetsuit eco-friendly?",
            "content": "<p>The Mentawai <strong>women’s wetsuit</strong> is made from a limestone-based eco-neoprene, which significantly reduces reliance on petroleum-based materials. The inside lining is crafted with GT3 recycled PET fabric, repurposing plastic waste and minimising our environmental footprint.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_pane_ce6DtQ": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Are these spring suits only for surfing and diving?",
            "content": "<p>Our spring suits are versatile and perfect for a range of water activities, including kitesurfing, paddleboarding, kayaking, and swimming. They are designed to move with your body, providing comfort, warmth and protection in any water adventure</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_pane_Py7J3k": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How do i care for my wetsuit?",
            "content": "<p>To keep your wetsuit in top condition, rinse it with fresh water after every use, especially after exposure to saltwater or chlorine. Then hang or lie flat in a shady area.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_pane_zwBQPA": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "settings": {
            "title": "IS 2.5mm good for surfers?",
            "content": "<p>Yes! A 2.5mm thickness is ideal for warmer waters and spring or summer surfing. It provides just the right amount of insulation to keep you warm without compromising flexibility, making it perfect for surfing, diving, and other water activities in moderate temperatures. This <strong>surfing wetsuit for women</strong> ensures you stay warm without feeling restricted.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_pane_ArMU9p": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Do limestone wetsuits crease easier than regular wetsuits?",
            "content": "<p>Being a memory foam, creasing is a normal part of the material properties. Wearing the wetsuit and letting it mould to your body will reduce the creases over time.</p><p></p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_pane_DK8Pq7": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "settings": {
            "title": "I'm not sure what size I am in wetsuit",
            "content": "<p>We have our size chart for the Neoprene <a href=\"https://www.oceansoulbali.com/pages/size-guide-wetsuits\" title=\"https://www.oceansoulbali.com/pages/size-guide-wetsuits\">here. </a></p><p>You can also reach out to us directly for further assistance via <a href=\"/pages/contact-us\" title=\"Contact Us\">email.</a></p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_pane_rUYgnW": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "title": "Can I return it if it's not the right size or if I don't like it?",
            "content": "<p>Absolutely!  We offer easy returns and exchanges. If your wetsuit isn’t the right size or doesn’t meet your expectations, you can return it for a refund or exchange. Please visit our <a href=\"#\">Shipping, Returns & Warranty</a> page for more details.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
